      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I have taken such meticulous care of it, and it still has that 'new car' magic. No scratches, no dents, and it drives like an absolute dream. I am sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall head over heels for it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
