      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine mechanical and cosmetic form. This specimen features the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, showcasing impeccable compression across all cylinders and a recently serviced dual-VANOS system. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is exceptional, with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension utilizing OEM bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. Heat cycling is managed by a recently overhauled cooling system including a high-flow water pump and aluminum radiator. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, free of fluid seepage or oxidation, reflecting its life in a climate-controlled environment. This is a turn-key enthusiast vehicle with no deferred maintenance.",
